# For Netlify or Cloudflare Pages: place this file named "_headers"
# in your published output directory (or project root for Netlify).
#
# Replace https://YOUR-NOMUOS-ORIGIN with the origin where NomuOS/Browie runs.
# If NomuOS is on the SAME origin as these pages, 'self' alone is enough.
#
# IMPORTANT: do NOT also send "X-Frame-Options" — it would override this and
# block embedding. Remove any X-Frame-Options you currently set.

/*
  Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'self' https://nomuos.imronaldmendoza.com
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload
